creator: FOOD ARMOUR INC
descriptionHtml:
Food Armour Driver App
This Driver application is used by food delivery drivers and couriers to Scan and Track outgoing food deliveries using Food Armour secure tracking devices.
Providing Food Delivery drivers and Food Delivery companies with 3rd party accountability.

Food Armour provides stores and customers with the peace of mind of safe secure food delivery.

1. With the Food Armour Driver application, drivers/couriers simply:

- download Driver app
- select the delivery company they are picking up for
- scan the security tag on their order pickup
- re-scan when arriving to the customer
- there is also a Driver assist to assist drivers with GPS and estimated time of arrival to customer


2. Food Armour is a Canadian based company which operates as a secure Food Delivery service, which provides Restaurants, Stores and Couriers with 3rd party accountability, to ensure a Tamper proof/Tamper evident food delivery to their Customers. This is done through the sophisticated yet simple to use Food Armour platform and Mobile apps.
The result is safe secure food delivery service for both customers and stores.

title: FA Driver - Peace of Mind From Store To Door
